            <tr>
              <td width="634" height="16" valign="top"><P class="statscontenttitle"><strong>OVERALL CRIME FELL BY 6.3%</strong>

</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="faqscontenttitle">
              <td height="16" valign="top"><p class="statscontenttext">In the first six-months of 2013, overall crime  reported fell by 6.3% to 14,562 cases as compared to 15,539 cases over the same  period last year. </p>
                <p class="statscontenttext">Four of  the six crime classes registered decreases. They are namely, <strong>Housebreaking and Related Crimes (-24.3%), Commercial Crimes  (-14.3%), Theft and Related Crimes (-6.8%) and Miscellaneous Crimes (-4.8%)</strong>. Improvements were seen in unlicensed moneylending and  phone scams, which were concerns highlighted for 2012. </p>
                <p class="statscontenttext">Two  crime classes registered increases. They are<strong> Crimes Against Persons (+ 5.3%)</strong> and <strong>Violent Property Crimes (+3.7%).</strong>                </p>
                <p class="statscontenttext"><strong>Table 1</strong>: <strong>BREAKDOWN OF OVERALL CRIME IN JAN-JUN 2012/2013</strong></p>
                <table width="572" border="1" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" valign="middle" nowrap bgcolor="#D9D9D9" class="statscontenttext"><strong>CRIME    CLASSES</strong></td>
                    <td width="85" valign="middle" nowrap bgcolor="#D9D9D9"><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>Jan-Jun 2012</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="85" valign="middle" nowrap bgcolor="#D9D9D9"><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>Jan-Jun 2013</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="57" valign="middle" nowrap bgcolor="#D9D9D9"><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>+/-</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="73" valign="middle" bgcolor="#D9D9D9"><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>% change</strong></p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272"><p class="statscontenttext">Housebreaking and    Related Crimes</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">333</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">252</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-81</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-24.3%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext">Commercial Crimes</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">1,841</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">1,577</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-264</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-14.3%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext">Theft and Related    Crimes</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">9,257</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">8,623</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-634</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-6.8%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext">Miscellaneous    Crimes</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">2,097</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">1,996</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-101</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">-4.8%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext">Crimes Against    Persons</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">1,821</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">1,917</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">96</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">5.3%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext">Violent Property    Crimes</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">190</p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">197</p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">7</p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext">3.7%</p></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td width="272" nowrap><p class="statscontenttext"><strong>OVERALL CRIME</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>15,539</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="85" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>14,562</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="57" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>-977</strong></p></td>
                    <td width="73" nowrap><p align="center" class="statscontenttext"><strong>-6.3%</strong></p></td>
                  </tr>
